  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is to evaluate the incidence of interstitial pneumonia in lymphoma patients&#xD;
      treated with liposomal doxorubucin. The treatment response and other adverse events will also&#xD;
      be studied.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
